49:19.387 --> 49:20.346
Yeah.

49:20.476 --> 49:22.144
Better let it run for a while.

49:22.301 --> 49:24.137
OK.

49:24.302 --> 49:26.513
Oh, wait.

49:26.695 --> 49:29.823
Here. This one's clean.

49:33.611 --> 49:35.487
I guess you better
get to work, huh?

49:35.655 --> 49:37.156
You're gonna be late.

49:37.308 --> 49:39.727
Yeah.

49:49.921 --> 49:52.340
Thank you, Jim.

50:05.406 --> 50:07.659
It was something
that just happened.

50:07.797 --> 50:09.716
Neither of us expected it.

50:09.886 --> 50:11.555
Neither of us planned it.

50:11.669 --> 50:15.090
But once we started, we knew
there was no turning back.

50:15.278 --> 50:18.823
It was a miracle.

50:19.064 --> 50:20.857
Oh, Jim.

50:31.895 --> 50:34.397
Hey, take me to that motel,

50:34.592 --> 50:35.676
like you wanted.

50:35.810 --> 50:37.395
Now?

50:37.549 --> 50:39.217
Um, come by after school.

50:39.376 --> 50:40.794
I'll leave Darryl with a sitter.

50:40.941 --> 50:43.694
