51:51.534 --> 51:52.618
Well, I tried you at home,

51:52.709 --> 51:54.461
and we've got a situation here.

51:54.621 --> 51:55.956
If Paul loses
this election tomorrow,

51:56.058 --> 51:57.225
there has to be another one

51:57.363 --> 51:58.531
with posters.

51:58.624 --> 52:00.501
