52:00.625 --> 52:02.126
Those posters cost
us a lot of money,

52:02.277 --> 52:03.403
and there's no time
to make any more.

52:03.538 --> 52:04.873
All right, we'll get
to the bottom of it.

52:05.016 --> 52:06.685
We still have some extra ones,
don't we?

52:06.844 --> 52:08.137
