that our actions,

55:21.573 --> 55:26.494
all of them, can carry
serious consequences.

55:26.748 --> 55:29.918
Mm-hmm. I don't know
what you're referring to,

55:30.096 --> 55:32.682
but maybe if certain
older, wiser people

55:32.882 --> 55:34.800
hadn't acted like such little babies

55:34.925 --> 55:36.051
and gotten so mushy,

55:36.187 --> 55:38.147
then everything would be OK.

55:38.274 --> 55:40.651
I agree, and I also think

55:40.840 --> 55:42.592
that certain young and naive people

55:42.754 --> 55:44.630
need to thank their lucky stars

55:44.799 --> 55:46.509
and be very, very grateful

55:46.668 --> 55:48.712
the entire school didn't find out

55:48.886 --> 55:50.221
about certain indiscretions

55:50.366 --> 55:52.701
that could've ruined
their reputations

